<i>noun</i>: 현대화 [현ː대화], 근대화 [근ː대화] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>현대화 [현ː대화]</dt><br>
<dd>modernization</dd><br>
<dd>현대에 꼭 알맞게 됨. 또는 그렇게 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of keeping up with modern times; or an act of making this happen.</dd><br>
<dt>근대화 [근ː대화]</dt><br>
<dd>modernization</dd><br>
<dd>사회와 문화 등이 근대의 특성을 받아들여 발전됨. 또는 그렇게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>Advancement in a society or culture by adopting the characteristics of modern times; the act of making this happen.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>